title: #90: Banks Suck (Tom Brady)
itunes:title: Banks Suck with Tom Brady
description: Tom Brady had me over to his house to help teach me about our economy. The more I learn about this stuff, the more I realize how little I know. Tom is an economist of sorts and he helps break a lot of it down in idiot stoner terms so I can start to understand.
